      "title": "Multiply the values",
      "content": "Evaluate and multiply.<br/>$$g(13a)=\\frac{-13a}{a}-12=-25$$<br/>$$g(8a)=\\frac{-8a}{a}-12=-20$$<br/>$$(-25)(-20)=500$$<br/>The answer is <strong>500</strong>."
